document_data.History:
It was established after [[1369 DR]]<ref>{{Cite dungeon/198/Cormyr Royale: The Royal Court of the Forest Kingdom}} by Royal Mage [[Vangerdahast Aeiulvana]], who erected the magical wall, and survived the [[Spellplague]]. It was originally built by the [[Irlingstar]] house of [[Waterdeep]] and then sold to Comryr.<ref>{{Cite dungeon/198/Cormyr Royale: The Royal Court of the Forest Kingdom}}

At one point before [[1385 DR]] the first prisoner was [[Amarune]], although she later escaped.{{Cite dungeon/206/Ecology of the Malaugrym|1-6}}<ref>{{Cite dungeon/198/Cormyr Royale: The Royal Court of the Forest Kingdom}}

In [[1480 DR]], a mysterious murder occurred inside the castle.
